rComments: Had 0 interest prior to attending as I'm an engineer and HPS was my elective. However, Mike's lectures truly helped me develop an interest in the material, and HPS turned out to be my favourite class of the semester. As a bonus, he responded to my email for help at 1 am! An amazing person - hope he gets a full-time position soon.

He's a newbie to teaching an entire course, but he makes the content interesting. Also, his knowledge of the content is impressive; barely says "I don't know" and if he does, he'll elaborate with his reasoning/interpretation. Overall, he's gonna be a great future prof.
